<node id="Article 16(2) TFEU">
  <data key="d0">Article 16(2) TFEU</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 16(2) TFEU mandates the European Parliament and the Council to establish rules concerning the protection of natural persons related to personal data processing.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e2d13a59890e903c4e56162458f272ab</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773018971</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="European Parliament">
  <data key="d0">European Parliament</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The European Parliament is one of the principal legislative bodies of the European Union (EU) and plays a vital role in the drafting, passing, and evaluation of regulations and directives that govern various aspects of European life. This institution is essential in establishing and interpreting laws related to public access to information, data privacy, and personal data protection. As the directly elected parliamentary institution within the EU, it collaborates with other key bodies such as the European Commission and the Council of the European Union, ensuring a comprehensive legislative process.

The European Parliament is actively involved in legislation that impacts a broad spectrum of sectors, including artificial intelligence (AI). It has contributed to key regulations such as Regulation (EU) 2024/1689 governing AI systems and participates in creating frameworks concerning cybersecurity requirements for products with digital elements. In addition to AI, the Parliament has enacted important directives, including the Unfair Commercial Practices Directive and the Directive on the Resilience of Critical Entities, effectively shaping the legal landscape across member states.

Engagement in the legislative process includes examining, amending, and adopting regulatory proposals, with oversight responsibilities that encompass reviewing reports concerning data protection submitted to it. The Parliament plays a significant role in the assessment and reporting on regulatory matters, ensuring that legislative measures are updated in alignment with contemporary challenges, thus safeguarding citizens' rights.

Moreover, the European Parliament is tasked with establishing various financial regulations and directives that affect credit institutions, as well as other legislative areas such as interoperability. By operating within a framework of oversight and representation, the Parliament not only passes essential laws but also serves as a crucial link between the EU's institutions and its citizens. This multi-faceted involvement underlines its integral position within the broader governance of the European Union.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2cbf3f86a25d11cd5d991d79db9a221a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76c97638c70c32faaac95c378d456ab2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9e09a4cc6243398f5e32d65a6312bd87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9bfe3c72af8b2bd319fe191920f25097&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5f087b1b4f7f6e16afe33b8014a5f30c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b5bb48441e5e8722f7d89d485c663d88&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58a23170492ef728683ec4aa9e03ccb4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e302930e155db8d2b9e787df655d5751&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b63383abdca30a6a477ed963f4766dc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b39c0bb45bd2a8849aa7e9bcb8c9d4a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a0ea41c30759ecd048ab40483ec1605b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-87ae75b9888750c7d94cfda6be4f3dac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c1a7de4ca41da4fd41e3254a6460114&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-088a4c3c3c775d33baa63868a127c869&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9238afdc9781d2e524a5550b3c165bed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-46bc64e87ac07d3576c10a8dd9d66d9e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7f5283f6c8ea50d5bcac79684f773610&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cfdd4a90d27a0fa7cfe5caacb375335c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-70bf47b2a9599482bedc275e3e2257a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea757da73e875c6fedacdd166bb91c2e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7078a625612fc9b62bb1e1986ffe1b7b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b084b4b20e358aaf88a17e35cc6da65d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5f6ef3b354bb0dbf8af7b2c108fd236&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e128fa4453175248aac2b8414bc17643&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f35759698835ddd7beb04c8f00f74f9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0cbd1a5d65f0da33dfc2d2c52c0fa26f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-837ff2237a4d4f4c44aa67702b89ec06&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4086e5336bfe9061f6ae69821c67e4ab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-24db102847abeef12e1042f8de042ea9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b64b4983aba9917221464e74b0d86865&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bc7122206f7a3097526258a05d85baef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2ab4686c3d64e748fcf2e50ddb488920&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d5a14698f71544a90fc06f98323f315&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0bbf5cbd8a6844b23704b7143707807&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-22207e9a20c55a3749a58440b8aab4fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3b1941526d498e207caabd2fb04f938f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab5bd61fedb2857e3db189c5f7bb8f94&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ad4d08daad55de411fe1304fd990b8e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4b4a84f46448cc3a4a1755da273e920e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6a7c04a6e62adc17c47006b55b3e8bce</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
