</node>
<node id="Administrative Costs">
  <data key="d0">Administrative Costs</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Administrative costs refer to the expenses incurred by the Supervisory Authority in processing requests that may be charged when they are excessive or unfounded.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8bb97fdc90c81e778311b34e1a2883b2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773018974</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Supervisory Authority">
  <data key="d0">Supervisory Authority</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Supervisory Authority is an independent public agency established in each Member State to monitor and enforce compliance with data protection regulations. It plays a crucial role in ensuring that data processing activities adhere to applicable laws, thereby protecting individual privacy rights.

As the competent entity, the Supervisory Authority is responsible for overseeing the application of data protection laws, providing guidance on compliance, and issuing measures to enforce these regulations. It is consulted during data processing risk assessments, can intervene in processing operations, and has the authority to impose penalties for infringements of these laws. Furthermore, the authority is charged with assessing processing operations and ensuring compliance with specific safeguards established by law.

An essential function of the Supervisory Authority includes facilitating communication between data subjects and data controllers. This body handles complaints from individuals regarding personal data processing, investigates these issues, and ensures that data subjects are informed of the progress of their complaints. Additionally, the authority is involved in cooperative efforts with other regulatory bodies to bolster data protection across jurisdictions.

The Supervisory Authority is also empowered to adopt provisional measures to safeguard the rights of data subjects, monitor adherence to codes of conduct by data processors, and maintain transparency in its operations by making requirements public in accessible formats. It drafts decisions on complaints and communicates its determinations within the legal framework guiding data protection.

Overall, the Supervisory Authority serves as a regulatory body vital to maintaining high standards of data protection compliance, establishing a clear structure for accountability, and enabling citizens to assert their data rights effectively within its jurisdiction.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6cef9a553db9271d5edd9d76997b31b8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ca204399e5b95988e550678c5f4db7ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1fc0f10aaf2165d757efc7d75a7d7d18&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47177763646868a685685b7567bea40f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3dec771ee61059f33dea3999f6d5facd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8bb97fdc90c81e778311b34e1a2883b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-89bcf919dc1ff2d224ffc9b6e042a2c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-18dac2bb6a1be4d5442954b82a769ffd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3ce3387b9f0e9256cf8b0a10e0726f37&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9552394e758f858742ece06fe166111&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-87f4c2229943d3f8e84a9941f117b8b1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da5e0cbe02b415c14c47d962922ae943&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe63429efbb90ae6ec22b62b5d79e7b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-51e09a8c8db52827f80f9874a8d4e4de&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e52d9f505adab3ccf36c6979ad3a7d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5f087b1b4f7f6e16afe33b8014a5f30c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3bbf8c83dfe1a6df2d3a3d01645abe8f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbc89674e06d04462cc498a8c1da1d44&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db7bcd6a42a9c26ced1d71444d109dff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-af9d06fe383d38e16d29be00a265867e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-af27fd67de6b968672bf93dbf11392ac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b5bb48441e5e8722f7d89d485c663d88&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e3626adc7cf865bec83f6479c1e08cb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e144d059e01c4df4d2fdb9406d31751d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7aa4d903bc5ead1fdb896356fd92fbd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8252fb4b704db3adac7bfb7714d3b70f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-274264435e41f5d230030900b38f8c35&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-df28c0bb060b598df163cc06bf49d0e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f71c70521bc1935b4a077373428f4b1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65949aed6696e22716296aea9c7eb380&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4fb6b788c6bc23206d8cd996c5a6a6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b1184185c4bc8012fe969516fa45f07b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ab41d6ec0d1446be5ba58c1ab5b423c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c22927198decad5ee173ab2f05d62983&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36a1ea945634c046899535f1e8f39a77</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773018974</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Data Protection Audits">
  <data key="d0">Data Protection Audits</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Data Protection Audits are investigations conducted by the Supervisory Authority to assess compliance with data protection regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8bb97fdc90c81e778311b34e1a2883b2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773018974</data>
