</node>
<node id="Profiling">
  <data key="d0">Profiling</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Profiling involves automated processing of personal data to evaluate certain aspects related to an individual, posing specific rights and transparency obligations for data subjects.&lt;SEP&gt;Profiling is a form of automated processing that evaluates personal data to predict aspects of the data subject, influencing decisions made about them.&lt;SEP&gt;Profiling involves automated processing of personal data to evaluate certain aspects related to a natural person.&lt;SEP&gt;Profiling is the automated processing of personal data to evaluate certain personal aspects relating to a natural person.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b303412f58783d3e4bc19dbad4e2a43c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9bfe3c72af8b2bd319fe191920f25097&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7e5e9be572ec001588771fa74ce45258&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4b86ca29202de00c1292db00c1efa4b</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773019172</data>
