<node id="Automated Decision-Making">
  <data key="d0">Automated Decision-Making</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Automated Decision-Making refers to processes where decisions are made without human involvement based on automated data analysis, affecting individuals legally or significantly.&lt;SEP&gt;Automated Decision-Making involves processing personal data to make decisions without human intervention, including the use of profiling.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b303412f58783d3e4bc19dbad4e2a43c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e144d059e01c4df4d2fdb9406d31751d</data>
