  <data key="d2">Article 67 addresses the exchange of information practices between supervisory authorities and the Board.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 67 pertains to the advisory forum related to the drafting of common specifications by the Commission.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 67 details the establishment and role of the Advisory Forum in relation to AI regulation.</data>
