<node id="Fundamental Rights">
  <data key="d0">Fundamental Rights</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Fundamental Rights encompass basic human rights that must be protected in relation to personal data processing.&lt;SEP&gt;Fundamental rights are basic human rights that are legally protected and must be upheld in all jurisdictions.&lt;SEP&gt;Fundamental rights include basic human rights that must be protected, such as privacy, non-discrimination, and the right to an effective remedy.&lt;SEP&gt;Fundamental rights are the basic human rights that should be protected and considered in the context of AI systems and their regulation.&lt;SEP&gt;Fundamental Rights include the legal rights ensuring protection against discrimination and other rights within the context of AI system usage.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7071cdf0dedffd1eaf46713ebddb9b1e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cc7a45c7f8eea9ab9297b5839c19c2a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5af0747da2a9f2783a1bde010a13814&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7aba082da5b9f8ab2defc1a7a725bef0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5772ed895bc8308d060b1975c2dd69d0</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773019187</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="International Organization">
  <data key="d0">International Organization</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">An international organization is an entity established by multiple countries that work together on common interests and objectives, often dealing with issues like humanitarian relief or development.&lt;SEP&gt;An International Organization refers to any organization established by a treaty or other agreement between sovereign states that may receive personal data.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7071cdf0dedffd1eaf46713ebddb9b1e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e144d059e01c4df4d2fdb9406d31751d</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773018980</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="European Data Protection Supervisor">
  <data key="d0">European Data Protection Supervisor</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The European Data Protection Supervisor (EDPS) is an independent authority established to ensure compliance with data protection laws across the European Union. The EDPS plays a critical role in overseeing data protection regulations, contributing to the activities of the Board, and providing secretariat support. It acts as a competent authority concerning various aspects of data protection, including market surveillance in compliance with Union law.

In the drafting of relevant regulations, the EDPS is actively consulted and provides opinions regarding the implications for data protection. The authority also holds specific voting rights on principles and rules that apply to Union institutions, reinforcing its influence and regulatory power in this domain. One of its primary responsibilities includes supervising Union institutions and agencies, which entails the authority to impose administrative fines for non-compliance with data protection laws.

The EDPS is also engaged in emerging areas such as artificial intelligence, ensuring adherence to privacy regulations within this context. It may establish AI regulatory sandboxes to facilitate understanding and compliance among Union institutions while recognizing the legal implications of such frameworks. Additionally, the EDPS acts as an observer at meetings of the European Artificial Intelligence Board, underscoring its focus on the intersection of data protection and AI oversight.

Through these various roles and responsibilities, the EDPS is pivotal in maintaining high standards of data protection and promoting accountability within European institutions and bodies.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7d95ad85f86f6e4a4771e8f92b0cbf27&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36a1ea945634c046899535f1e8f39a77&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-af9d06fe383d38e16d29be00a265867e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b39c0bb45bd2a8849aa7e9bcb8c9d4a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-663826fe1821a9ef057cd84da3b741a8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f4b86ca29202de00c1292db00c1efa4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b45385ec456bd2744fcc58cd02368fc0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-382f1c7a3c02bab4bf3bee2d03cc7e1f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f40b01fb5e1dbaa442b55c31285ecb50&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f743aee05d8e1afc03000436802a1ad2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b28096d582da2417ada6ecd24c88d994&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3d055d5f99b33b0d67edb91e844c4185&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-77f7e4da7918161a180fb26c5a1704ff</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773019173</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
