  <data key="d0">Article 91</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 91 covers the data protection rules applicable to churches and religious associations in relation to the processing of personal data.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 91 pertains to the requests for documents or information that must be complied with by providers of general-purpose AI models.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a8ea5b2826564cb4f4f5c8c193fab368&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-382f1c7a3c02bab4bf3bee2d03cc7e1f</data>
