<node id="Article 92">
  <data key="d0">Article 92</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 92 outlines the requirements for presenting information by icons and the procedures for standardized icons.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 92 details the exercise of delegated acts and implementing acts regarding the Regulation.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 92 is referenced in relation to evaluations leading to concerns about systemic risks at the Union level.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a8ea5b2826564cb4f4f5c8c193fab368&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8252fb4b704db3adac7bfb7714d3b70f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f137cf6069f0720a443c5b5abd0fe3ea</data>
