  <data key="d0">Article 8</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 8 outlines the conditions applicable to a child's consent in relation to information society services.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 8 of Regulation (EU) No 182/2011, in conjunction with Article 5, pertains to the committee's operational procedures.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 8 outlines the compliance requirements for high-risk AI systems with respect to their intended purpose and technical standards.</data>
