<node id="Directive 2002/58/EC">
  <data key="d0">Directive 2002/58/EC</data>
  <data key="d1">regulation</data>
  <data key="d2">Directive 2002/58/EC outlines specific obligations regarding the processing of personal data and should be amended for consistency with the new Regulation.&lt;SEP&gt;Directive 2002/58/EC is a legal framework concerning the processing of personal data and the protection of privacy in electronic communications.&lt;SEP&gt;Directive 2002/58/EC is an important regulation regarding privacy and electronic communications, mentioned in the context of the data subject's rights.&lt;SEP&gt;Directive 2002/58/EC relates to the processing of personal data and privacy in the electronic communications sector.&lt;SEP&gt;Directive 2002/58/EC regulates the processing of personal data in the electronic communications sector.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-58a23170492ef728683ec4aa9e03ccb4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b39c0bb45bd2a8849aa7e9bcb8c9d4a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9d92eec8ceb3813d55e2b578c5604f24&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c1a7de4ca41da4fd41e3254a6460114&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-74667d89df5ee6111b7743e86ee4744f</data>
