<node id="Union Institutions">
  <data key="d0">Union Institutions</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Union institutions include various bodies of the European Union that handle legal acts and data protection matters.&lt;SEP&gt;Union institutions include the various bodies and authorities within the European Union that govern laws and regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Union institutions include various agencies and bodies within the European Union involved in regulation and enforcement.&lt;SEP&gt;Union institutions include organizations and agencies that operate under relevant Union laws and regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Union institutions are bodies or organizations that operate on behalf of the political union, engaging in decision making and governance processes.</data>
