<node id="Official Journal of the European Union">
  <data key="d0">Official Journal of the European Union</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The Official Journal of the European Union is the publication in which legislative acts and regulations are officially published.&lt;SEP&gt;The Official Journal of the European Union is the publication through which EU legislation and important decisions are officially communicated.&lt;SEP&gt;The Official Journal of the European Union publishes references to standards and regulations that must be adhered to by conformity assessment bodies.&lt;SEP&gt;The Official Journal of the European Union publishes legal texts and acts, including references to harmonised standards.</data>
