<node id="Article 9">
  <data key="d0">Article 9</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 9 deals with the processing of special categories of personal data and outlines exceptions to their processing restrictions.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 9 refers to a section in legal documents that outlines special categories of personal data and the conditions for processing such data.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 9 defines the risk management system that must be established for high-risk AI systems, outlining processes for risk identification and evaluation.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 9 refers to a specific provision within Regulation (EU) 2016/679 concerning the processing of personal data.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 9 of Regulation (EU) 2019/1020 outlines specific obligations related to market oversight for authorities concerning AI systems and other regulated areas.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3fa893844a2197c46302e74437f2bbef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c09ea8bbba955df15eafbe1da5facb38&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a242b3e1d633e7e955057a9b078f32d2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e87d6d03ced0c44c2805ed7127eb0258&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-880ccb1f68ffcae0925e238408590ede</data>
