</node>
<node id="Article 41">
  <data key="d0">Article 41</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 41 relates to the monitoring of compliance with approved codes of conduct.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 41 outlines the common specifications that providers may refer to for conformity assessment procedures.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 41 specifies common specifications related to AI technologies and their compliance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-65949aed6696e22716296aea9c7eb380&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9a54b012266e9b9c7302fce6d400f583&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-60ded1802882124212402df3d80de903&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-413f3509ccce7d84f0a2044eb12be69f</data>
