<node id="Council of the European Union">
  <data key="d0">Council of the European Union</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Council of the European Union is a fundamental decision-making body within the European Union (EU) that collaborates with the European Parliament to pass legislation and implement policies. It plays a crucial role in the legislative process, where it is involved in the approval and adoption of various laws, directives, and regulations that affect the member states.

The Council represents the governments of EU member states and acts on their behalf during legislative matters. It is particularly engaged in the legislative efforts that involve pivotal regulations, such as Regulation (EU) 2024/1689 concerning specific regulatory frameworks and cybersecurity measures. Additionally, the Council contributes to adopting directives like Directive (EU) 2019/790, which may pertain to copyright and intellectual property, highlighting its diverse involvement across multiple legislative areas.

Through its decision-making responsibilities, the Council of the European Union engages in discussions and negotiations alongside the European Parliament, ensuring that the interests and policies reflect the collective will of the member states. The institution's role extends beyond legislation as it also participates in implementing policies related to standardization and interoperability, thereby shaping the operational framework of the EU.

In summary, the Council of the European Union is an essential entity that facilitates legislative processes and decision-making in collaboration with the European Parliament, embodying the interests of EU member states in a wide array of regulatory and policy matters.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-87ae75b9888750c7d94cfda6be4f3dac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-70bf47b2a9599482bedc275e3e2257a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea757da73e875c6fedacdd166bb91c2e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e128fa4453175248aac2b8414bc17643&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-837ff2237a4d4f4c44aa67702b89ec06&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-24db102847abeef12e1042f8de042ea9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b64b4983aba9917221464e74b0d86865&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0bbf5cbd8a6844b23704b7143707807&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-22207e9a20c55a3749a58440b8aab4fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ab5bd61fedb2857e3db189c5f7bb8f94</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773019208</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
