  <data key="d0">Deceased Persons</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Deceased persons refer to individuals who have passed away, and specific regulations stipulate that certain laws do not apply to their personal data.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6ce0488d21ac5956f37974d7ae0799b4</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773018990</data>
