  <data key="d0">Widespread Medical Conditions</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Widespread medical conditions refer to commonly occurring health issues like cardiovascular disease, cancer, and depression, which can be studied through registries.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6ce0488d21ac5956f37974d7ae0799b4</data>
