<node id="Real-World Testing Plan">
  <data key="d0">Real-World Testing Plan</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A real-world testing plan outlines the objectives and methodologies for testing AI systems in actual conditions.&lt;SEP&gt;The Real-World Testing Plan is a structured approach for conducting tests of high-risk AI systems in real-world conditions, as mandated by Union regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f4b86ca29202de00c1292db00c1efa4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eced97c6a138205573883808dbd74066</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773019172</data>
