<node id="National Data Protection Authority">
  <data key="d0">National Data Protection Authority</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">National data protection authorities monitor compliance with data protection laws related to the use of biometric identification systems.&lt;SEP&gt;The National Data Protection Authority is responsible for ensuring compliance with data protection laws and regulations within a Member State.&lt;SEP&gt;The National Data Protection Authority is the entity tasked with enforcing data protection laws and ensuring compliance at the national level.</data>
