  <data key="d0">Annual Reports</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Annual reports provide an aggregation of data on the use of biometric identification systems by Member States for law enforcement.&lt;SEP&gt;Annual reports are documents submitted by national competent authorities detailing the progress and results of AI regulatory sandboxes.</data>
