<node id="Competent Authorities">
  <data key="d0">Competent Authorities</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Competent authorities are organizations or bodies responsible for overseeing compliance with regulations and ensuring safety and rights.&lt;SEP&gt;Competent authorities are organizations or bodies designated to grant authorizations related to AI systems and law enforcement as per the regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Competent authorities are regulatory bodies responsible for ensuring compliance with the regulations related to high-risk AI systems.&lt;SEP&gt;Competent authorities are regulatory bodies responsible for overseeing the compliance and safety of high-risk AI systems in the market.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3642f938e14bfed60a5d5b5fdc383e38&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d17f49a76bb2cf6b427b715f614df19&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c3976a157910b9837b3b68c158c5b6b9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b5da5d9be8aadcb05915f4a8f8f5aa33</data>
