<node id="Article 78">
  <data key="d0">Article 78</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 78 discusses obligations related to confidentiality of information obtained by notifying authorities.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 78 addresses confidentiality obligations related to sensitive information obtained under this regulation.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 78 outlines confidentiality obligations for the Commission and market surveillance authorities concerning the handling of sensitive information.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-80e46c2caec4056bbc2d3b305e3ed190&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe99ac2ad30ad5f2f6c6c5e2e23456e9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ba035757525dfa257fa2b97fdbd40b2</data>
