  <data key="d0">National Public Authorities</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">National public authorities are local governmental entities responsible for overseeing the application of Union law at the national level.&lt;SEP&gt;National Public Authorities are the local governing bodies within member states that oversee compliance with EU regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;National Public Authorities are government bodies in each Member State responsible for overseeing the implementation of regulations and maintaining confidentiality regarding sensitive information.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-80e46c2caec4056bbc2d3b305e3ed190&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-088a4c3c3c775d33baa63868a127c869&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f40b01fb5e1dbaa442b55c31285ecb50</data>
