<node id="Regulation (EU) 2018/1139">
  <data key="d0">Regulation (EU) 2018/1139</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Regulation (EU) 2018/1139 establishes rules for civil aviation and the European Union Aviation Safety Agency.&lt;SEP&gt;Regulation (EU) 2018/1139 is subjected to amendments in Regulation (EU) 2024/1689.&lt;SEP&gt;Regulation (EU) 2018/1139 establishes common rules in the field of civil aviation and is amended to incorporate AI considerations.&lt;SEP&gt;Regulation (EU) 2018/1139 sets forth common rules in civil aviation and establishes the European Union Aviation Safety Agency.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6089fa3fb8ca9e6804e31c89a758b4ff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7078a625612fc9b62bb1e1986ffe1b7b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0bb1522a7ffbcc317a23b095e16b092&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-971ebc9330032c79166b56276164406c</data>
