  <data key="d0">Regulation (EU) 2019/2144</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Regulation (EU) 2019/2144 pertains to vehicle safety, addressing AI systems as crucial components in modern automotive technology.&lt;SEP&gt;Regulation (EU) 2019/2144 sets type-approval requirements for motor vehicles and their safety mechanisms.&lt;SEP&gt;Regulation (EU) 2019/2144 is amended by Regulation (EU) 2024/1689.&lt;SEP&gt;Regulation (EU) 2019/2144 addresses the type approval of motor vehicles and trailer regulations, including provisions for AI components.&lt;SEP&gt;Regulation (EU) 2019/2144 sets type-approval requirements for motor vehicles, ensuring safety and protection for vehicle occupants.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6089fa3fb8ca9e6804e31c89a758b4ff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7078a625612fc9b62bb1e1986ffe1b7b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0bb1522a7ffbcc317a23b095e16b092&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0cbd1a5d65f0da33dfc2d2c52c0fa26f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2ab4686c3d64e748fcf2e50ddb488920</data>
