  <data key="d2">The European Artificial Intelligence Board is responsible for supporting the Commission in promoting AI literacy and understanding among the public.&lt;SEP&gt;The European Artificial Intelligence Board (the 'Board') consults on guidelines provided by the Commission regarding AI systems.&lt;SEP&gt;The European Artificial Intelligence Board is established to advise and assist in the application of regulations related to AI across Member States.</data>
