  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The risk management system refers to procedures that ensure compliance and mitigate risks associated with high-risk AI systems.&lt;SEP&gt;The Risk Management System is a framework for identifying, assessing, and mitigating potential risks associated with AI systems.</data>
