  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 50 pertains to compliance measures related to AI systems.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 50 addresses transparency obligations for providers and deployers within the regulatory framework.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 50 pertains to specific provisions within the Regulation regarding AI systems that require additional transparency measures.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 50 refers to a specific provision related to transparency measures within regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9a54b012266e9b9c7302fce6d400f583&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b45385ec456bd2744fcc58cd02368fc0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5f6ef3b354bb0dbf8af7b2c108fd236&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f35759698835ddd7beb04c8f00f74f9a</data>
