<node id="High-Risk AI System">
  <data key="d0">High-Risk AI System</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">High-Risk AI Systems are defined as artificial intelligence technologies that have been categorized due to their potential to pose significant risks to safety, fundamental rights, and public welfare. These systems necessitate specific risk management protocols and compliance measures in accordance with established regulations. The identification of high-risk AI systems mandates comprehensive governance arrangements and thorough conformity assessments to ensure that they meet required safety standards before being allowed in the market.

These systems impose substantial obligations on developers and organizations involved in their creation and deployment, requiring strict oversight to mitigate risks associated with health, safety, and biases. High-risk AI systems must be subjected to detailed impact assessments to evaluate their implications on users and society at large. The regulations guiding these assessments are designed to foster accountability and adherence to quality management standards.

Furthermore, high-risk AI systems are characterized by their significant implications for public safety, necessitating rigorous scrutiny to prevent or minimize risks. The overarching goal of these regulatory measures is to ensure the responsible use of AI technologies, protecting individuals and communities from potential adverse effects related to their deployment.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-80e46c2caec4056bbc2d3b305e3ed190&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-92f9c6220442ff06dfe6fe52499f18aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e42c3bff7bd9447d59998364274b31d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd94ba8542b0c8ff4b050fc6027f5237&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e318b5cf27cebec499fc2e251461775a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c2fbe724dee488ea4e437995307241f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-234952a50b5a02b1afedbe8d8e1c076b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3ca50c2792c184b300a7d258f980e38c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d17f49a76bb2cf6b427b715f614df19&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-70bf47b2a9599482bedc275e3e2257a5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c3976a157910b9837b3b68c158c5b6b9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea757da73e875c6fedacdd166bb91c2e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-474ee56c196aef9638f343ef09589bca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20cc9868fcea5ce578101b36c79a42ff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5a13415ed2c222ba72d78fdab855a6ca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-880ccb1f68ffcae0925e238408590ede&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-93ef23a1d24ffc516addd681974bac32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1d997baeb2a2ac2118ac1e3e19dfcf16&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f0714fdb65a0577bc4493dcb81d0a915&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-60ded1802882124212402df3d80de903&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b14c58587932db3a6dafb07fe1b8b673&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-741b1675a971d075b2d3571148530b89&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf7d18a6020405fb3429834a129e7cd0</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
