  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Directive 2013/32/EU is a directive from the European Parliament aimed at providing common procedures for granting and withdrawing international protection.&lt;SEP&gt;Directive 2013/32/EU pertains to common procedures for granting and withdrawing international protection, set by the European Parliament and Council.</data>
