<node id="Risk-Management System">
  <data key="d0">Risk-Management System</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Risk-management systems aim to identify and mitigate risks associated with high-risk AI systems, ensuring health, safety, and rights.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e42c3bff7bd9447d59998364274b31d5</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773019195</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="New Legislative Framework">
  <data key="d0">New Legislative Framework</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The New Legislative Framework refers to a set of EU regulations aimed at ensuring consistent compliance and safety standards across various sectors, particularly regarding product regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;The New Legislative Framework provides guidelines for legislative actions in the context of European Union law.&lt;SEP&gt;The New Legislative Framework encompasses updated EU regulatory measures and guidelines for product compliance, including those incorporating AI systems.&lt;SEP&gt;The New Legislative Framework refers to a set of requirements aiming to ensure the consistency and quality of products and services across the European Union, with specific relevance to the regulation of high-risk AI systems.&lt;SEP&gt;The New Legislative Framework refers to EU legislation aimed at ensuring consistent safety standards and market access for products, including AI systems.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e42c3bff7bd9447d59998364274b31d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e99d990c855f3b544868eeee8a6b049b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea757da73e875c6fedacdd166bb91c2e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bc7122206f7a3097526258a05d85baef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-00803764d58d840979922e38d1dc555c</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773019195</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
