  <data key="d0">Regulation (EU) No 1025/2012</data>
  <data key="d1">regulation</data>
  <data key="d2">Regulation (EU) No 1025/2012 outlines rules regarding European standardisation, relevant to the compliance requirements of various regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Regulation (EU) No 1025/2012 establishes requirements for standardisation in the EU.&lt;SEP&gt;Regulation (EU) No 1025/2012 outlines the procedures for the development and adoption of harmonised standards within the EU.&lt;SEP&gt;Regulation (EU) No 1025/2012 provides guidelines on the development and compliance of European standards for products.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-38cdce9b64b40ba40d6acb529d375787&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-926dc457d536779e13715d0b813c320d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-837ff2237a4d4f4c44aa67702b89ec06&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bfb1222254442ec5ae96316c08a386f0</data>
