<node id="SMEs">
  <data key="d0">SMEs</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">SMEs (Small and Medium-sized Enterprises) are businesses that play a crucial role in the economy and are often providers or deployers of AI systems.&lt;SEP&gt;SMEs (Small and Medium-sized Enterprises) are businesses that can participate in AI regulatory sandboxes, benefiting from guidance and resources provided to promote their growth and innovation.&lt;SEP&gt;SMEs refer to small and medium-sized enterprises that are targeted for support in accessing AI regulatory sandboxes and complying with regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;SMEs (Small and Medium-sized Enterprises) are businesses that the Commission considers when developing guidelines, focusing on their needs in relation to AI.&lt;SEP&gt;SMEs refer to Small and Medium-sized Enterprises, which are subject to administrative fines under the regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b75f7d42df244a78773a748afb4f421f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b45385ec456bd2744fcc58cd02368fc0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d5a14698f71544a90fc06f98323f315&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b28096d582da2417ada6ecd24c88d994&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7e4463f7eaf425919a6a8182d693643c</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773019201</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Guidelines">
  <data key="d0">Guidelines</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Guidelines are detailed instructions developed by the Commission regarding the practical implementation of regulations governing AI systems.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b75f7d42df244a78773a748afb4f421f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773019201</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quality Management System">
  <data key="d0">Quality Management System</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Quality Management System is a framework required for compliance, which microenterprises must establish in a simplified manner.&lt;SEP&gt;The Quality Management System is a structured system that ensures compliance of high-risk AI systems with relevant regulations and standards.&lt;SEP&gt;The Quality Management System consists of guidelines aimed at ensuring protection and compliance related to high-risk AI systems, particularly for microenterprises.&lt;SEP&gt;The Quality Management System ensures that the processes and standards for the AI System's development and assessment are adequately followed.&lt;SEP&gt;The Quality Management System is a framework that ensures providers comply with specified quality standards and practices.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3ca50c2792c184b300a7d258f980e38c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-741b1675a971d075b2d3571148530b89&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d2a58a86edb7bec623750da3d232aa2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-15ddf6f50e7dd1750489a4999454bcdf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-77f7e4da7918161a180fb26c5a1704ff</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773019201</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
