<node id="Article 112">
  <data key="d0">Article 112</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 112 focuses on the evaluation and review processes related to the Regulation.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 112 describes the evaluation and review process for assessing AI regulations and their applicability over time.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b084b4b20e358aaf88a17e35cc6da65d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-413f3509ccce7d84f0a2044eb12be69f</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1773019209</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 46(1)">
  <data key="d0">Article 46(1)</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 46(1) refers to a regulation that may exempt deployers from the obligation to notify.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fe99ac2ad30ad5f2f6c6c5e2e23456e9</data>
