  <data key="d0">Conformity Assessment Activities</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Conformity assessment activities encompass various evaluations and certifications performed by conformity assessment bodies to verify compliance with standards.&lt;SEP&gt;Conformity assessment activities involve the evaluation conducted by notified bodies to ensure compliance with regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1d997baeb2a2ac2118ac1e3e19dfcf16&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6507d56efb6357f20f57227d44b681ea</data>
