<node id="Criminal Offences">
  <data key="d0">Criminal Offences</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Criminal offences are actions punishable by law, one of which could justify the use of biometric identification in law enforcement scenarios.&lt;SEP&gt;Criminal offences refer to various unlawful acts such as terrorism, human trafficking, and murder, as detailed in legislation.</data>
