  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Annex VI outlines the internal control procedures applicable to the assessment of high-risk AI systems’ compliance.&lt;SEP&gt;Annex VI includes internal control procedures applicable for assessing high-risk AI systems.&lt;SEP&gt;Annex VI details internal control measures for preventing or minimizing risks associated with AI systems.</data>
