  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Conformity Assessment is a procedure to demonstrate whether a product or system meets specified requirements, especially for high-risk AI systems.&lt;SEP&gt;Conformity assessment is the process of demonstrating whether specific requirements for high-risk AI systems have been fulfilled.</data>
