  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The World Trade Organization is an international organization that regulates trade between nations and aims to ensure that trade flows as smoothly and predictably as possible.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Trade Organization is an international body that regulates trade and promotes mutual recognition of conformity assessment results among member nations.</data>
