<node id="Transparency Obligations">
  <data key="d0">Transparency Obligations</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Transparency obligations refer to requirements for AI providers and deployers to disclose when content is artificially generated or manipulated, ensuring accountability.&lt;SEP&gt;Transparency obligations stipulate that providers of AI systems must inform users when they are interacting with AI, ensuring clarity about the nature of the interaction.</data>
