<node id="Codes of Practice">
  <data key="d0">Codes of Practice</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Codes of practice are guidelines established for AI providers to ensure compliance and proper application of regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Codes of Practice are guidelines that may be relied upon by providers to demonstrate compliance with obligations related to systemic risks.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-13766dce116c63c31fc5d746b27279fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5ba035757525dfa257fa2b97fdbd40b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed27aea701ddc7f366ea5adbe8a4b8e8</data>
