  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 98 outlines the procedural framework for the adoption of implementing acts by the Commission.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 98 outlines the examination procedure related to the adoption of implementing acts for AI regulatory sandboxes.</data>
