  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Directive (EU) 2016/97 contains rules related to insurance distribution aimed at protecting consumers.&lt;SEP&gt;Directive (EU) 2016/97 concerns insurance distribution regulations established by the European Parliament and Council.</data>
