  <data key="d2">Stakeholders include individuals or groups engaged in the development and use of AI systems, encompassing industry, academia, civil society, and standardization organizations.&lt;SEP&gt;Stakeholders refer to individuals or groups that have an interest in the outcomes of the discussions and regulations regarding AI systems.</data>
