  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">Directive 2005/29/EC is a legislation intended to prevent unfair commercial practices leading to financial harms to consumers.&lt;SEP&gt;Directive 2005/29/EC pertains to unfair business practices within the internal market, aiming to protect consumers.</data>
