<node id="Regulation (EU) 2023/988">
  <data key="d0">Regulation (EU) 2023/988</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Regulation (EU) 2023/988 serves as a safety net for AI systems that are not classified as high-risk but are required to be safe for market entry.&lt;SEP&gt;Regulation (EU) 2023/988 is legislation from the European Parliament and Council on general product safety, affecting compliance and enforcement related to AI systems and other regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4996cfa66f0668d565cd83bbe46dd21a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ad4d08daad55de411fe1304fd990b8e3</data>
