  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The European Arrest Warrant is a legal framework that facilitates the extradition of individuals between Member States, established by Council Framework Decision 2002/584/JHA.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4b4a84f46448cc3a4a1755da273e920e</data>
