  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The European Parliament collaborates with the Council to make decisions regarding EU laws and regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;The European Parliament and the Council both have significant roles in the legislative process and may oppose or revoke delegated powers.&lt;SEP&gt;The European Parliament works in cooperation with the Council in the legislative process of the European Union.</data>
