  <data key="d7">6.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Commission provides relevant documents to the Council during the implementation of regulation.&lt;SEP&gt;The Council collaborates with the Commission in the execution of EU policies and decision-making.&lt;SEP&gt;The Commission collaborates with the Council in the legislative process and on various regulatory matters.&lt;SEP&gt;The Commission takes into consideration the positions of the Council during the legislative process.&lt;SEP&gt;The Council works with the Commission to enact legislation affecting all member states.&lt;SEP&gt;The Council receives simultaneous notification from the Commission regarding any delegated acts that are adopted.</data>
  <data key="d9">consultation,decision-making,document sharing,executive authority,governance,legislative collaboration,legislative process,member state representation,notification,regulatory process</data>
