  <data key="d8">Member States are subject to regulations set forth by the European Union.&lt;SEP&gt;Each Member State must adhere to the Regulation regarding data protection and supervisory authority tasks.&lt;SEP&gt;Member States must comply with the regulations set forth by the European Union regarding data protection.</data>
