<edge source="Member State" target="Union">
  <data key="d7">9.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation known as Member State, Union refers to the collective of various Member States that form part of a larger Union characterized by shared laws and policies. This Union serves as a governing body under which Member States are required to operate. Each Member State must comply with the Union's regulations and authority, embracing a unified framework that governs their interactions and obligations.

Member States collaborate within the Union to pursue important objectives that serve public interests, ensuring their joint effort contributes positively to broader societal goals. The Union provides the necessary framework within which these Member States can establish their own specific laws, notably in areas such as data protection. While each Member State retains the ability to create its own legislative measures, these must align with the overarching regulatory framework established by the Union.

Furthermore, all Member States operate within the guidelines set forth by the Union, which includes ensuring compliance with laws related to data processing and protection. Each Member State's adherence to these regulations is critical for effective administration and enforcement of such laws, which are part of the collective governance structure aimed at enhancing data security and public trust.

In summary, the Member State, Union relationship embodies a cooperative governance model where individual Member States function under the Union's authority, contributing to and adhering to shared legal frameworks for various regulatory domains, particularly in data processing activities.</data>
  <data key="d9">authority,cooperative governance,governance,governmental relationship,jurisdiction,legal compliance,legal framework,membership,political entity,political structure,regulation,territorial governance</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-bd97dcdb68144953a81ad8ba7d8f52b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e0789b58f298ba801f3b269230a509b8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-66ded376bcd1c12c425bce88cfd552a0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1e52d9f505adab3ccf36c6979ad3a7d0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db7bcd6a42a9c26ced1d71444d109dff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4816e09d93a70dec7bd3be2be787d180&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-40ecaa725d6d1bc748899703ed8b84dc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7e5e9be572ec001588771fa74ce45258</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773019025</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
