<edge source="Regulation" target="Member States">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Member States must adhere to the Regulation to ensure compliance in the processing of personal data.&lt;SEP&gt;The Regulation is binding in its entirety and must be complied with by all Member States.&lt;SEP&gt;Member States are responsible for supporting and facilitating the execution of the Regulation at national levels.&lt;SEP&gt;Member States must comply with the Regulation in the development and enforcement of AI guidelines.</data>
  <data key="d9">adherence,binding authority,compliance,facilitation,governance,legal obligations,membership</data>
