  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The new Regulation will prompt amendments to Directive 2002/58/EC to ensure consistency in data processing regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;The Regulation relates to Directive 2002/58/EC by necessitating amendments to ensure alignment.</data>
