<edge source="Personal Data" target="Controller">
  <data key="d7">8.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation known as "Controller" in the context of Personal Data refers to the entity charged with the management and processing of personal data, ensuring adherence to legal and regulatory requirements. The Controller plays a central role in overseeing personal data, with a primary responsibility to act in accordance with both consent from data subjects and established legal obligations.

The Controller's responsibilities include determining the methods and purposes for processing personal data, alongside maintaining compliance with privacy regulations. This requires a proactive approach to ensure that all actions taken in the handling of personal data uphold accountability and meet the standards set forth by applicable laws. As part of their duties, Controllers must manage data processing activities while being mindful of the rights and privacy of the data subjects involved.

Overall, the role of the Controller is integral to the safeguarding of personal data, necessitating a thorough understanding of the legal frameworks governing data protection and a commitment to fulfilling all obligations associated with data processing activities. This encompasses not only compliance with existing regulations but also the implementation of practices that promote transparency and trust.</data>
  <data key="d9">accountability,compliance,data handling,data management,data processing,legal compliance,processing obligation,responsibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-bd97dcdb68144953a81ad8ba7d8f52b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9bfe3c72af8b2bd319fe191920f25097&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b661d0b109eaf570a61ae0d0ca8020b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4816e09d93a70dec7bd3be2be787d180&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-62b277bc6fa564a434a6c338a48eea46&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-35884c5ef57faf321ff9fce99bd2d970&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2016931a6e14615018d3d7f8304b6a1e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9355b1cd3c48988b8332485ef99af2c3</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773019025</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Personal Data" target="Data Subject">
  <data key="d7">5.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The data subject has rights concerning the processing of their personal data, which must be respected.&lt;SEP&gt;The data subject is entitled to access and control their personal data which has been collected regarding them.&lt;SEP&gt;Data subjects have rights concerning the processing of their personal data, which must be respected by data controllers.&lt;SEP&gt;Personal Data pertains to the information collected relating to a Data Subject.&lt;SEP&gt;Personal Data is any information that relates to a Data Subject, detailing privacy concerns during processing.</data>
  <data key="d9">data collection,data processing,data rights,identification,individual privacy,information type,privacy,processing,rights</data>
