<edge source="Data Protection Officer" target="Controller">
  <data key="d7">7.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Data Protection Officer oversees the Controller's compliance with data protection regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;The Data Protection Officer oversees the compliance of the Controller regarding personal data processing.&lt;SEP&gt;Data Protection Officer oversees the data protection compliance of the controller.&lt;SEP&gt;The data protection officer plays an important role in advising the controller on data protection practices and compliance with regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;The controller seeks the advice of the data protection officer while performing data protection impact assessments and ensuring compliance.&lt;SEP&gt;The Controller must designate a Data Protection Officer responsible for ensuring adherence to data protection laws.&lt;SEP&gt;The Controller is responsible for ensuring the involvement of the Data Protection Officer in data protection matters.</data>
