<edge source="Supervisory Authority" target="Article 58">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Supervisory Authority may utilize the powers outlined in Article 58 for ensuring compliance with data protection regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 58 provides a framework for the powers and responsibilities of the Supervisory Authority in relation to data protection.&lt;SEP&gt;The Supervisory Authority exercises powers as described in Article 58 concerning data protection.</data>
  <data key="d9">compliance,enforcement,powers,regulatory framework,regulatory powers</data>
