<edge source="Data Subject" target="Automated Processing">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Automated processing can significantly impact data subjects, leading to evaluations that affect them legally or materially.&lt;SEP&gt;The Data Subject is affected by decisions made through Automated Processing, which does not involve human operation.</data>
  <data key="d9">automation,evaluation,impact,personal impact</data>
