</edge>
<edge source="Data Subject" target="Automated Decision-Making">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Automated Decision-Making can influence the legal status or rights of the Data Subject based on automated processes without human intervention.&lt;SEP&gt;Automated Decision-Making may impact the Data Subject's rights and privacy, requiring transparency and accountability.</data>
  <data key="d9">data rights,decision influence,legal effects,privacy impact</data>
