  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The data subject can invoke the right to be forgotten to remove their personal data from online platforms under specified circumstances.&lt;SEP&gt;The Data Subject can invoke the Right to be Forgotten to erase their personal data from processing.</data>
  <data key="d9">data control,data rights,privacy,privacy rights</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-5b661d0b109eaf570a61ae0d0ca8020b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ca37d7dbc74be645fc1de3e6e772a586</data>
