</edge>
<edge source="Data Subject" target="Data Controller">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Data controllers are responsible for processing and respecting the rights of data subjects.&lt;SEP&gt;The Data Controller must safeguard the rights of the Data Subject during the processing of personal data.</data>
