<edge source="Natural Persons" target="AI Systems">
  <data key="d7">7.0</data>
  <data key="d8">AI systems can impact the rights and behaviours of natural persons, potentially leading to exploitation.&lt;SEP&gt;Natural persons are subject to profiling and behavioral assessments using AI systems under certain regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;AI systems can significantly impact the rights of natural persons in legal contexts, particularly related to law enforcement and migration.&lt;SEP&gt;Natural persons' rights and freedoms can be adversely affected by AI systems as regulated by this legislation.&lt;SEP&gt;Natural persons are evaluated and classified by AI systems based on their distinct characteristics and behaviors.&lt;SEP&gt;AI systems are designed to interact with and assess the needs and behaviors of natural persons in various contexts.&lt;SEP&gt;Natural persons apply for various statuses, such as asylum or residency, with AI systems assessing their eligibility.</data>
  <data key="d9">eligible applications,evaluation,human interaction,impact,legal context,personal data,profiling,protection,rights,rights impact,rights protection,subject,technology application</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-62c64f05f2da893351ea92b9eac1c889&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e47ed52d4514f1818e6c0687c1aa57e4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4d44ed9cdcce8d29cd4cf7a4556478e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e64e0ad4efda4fc9f3a84823cb301955&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-00803764d58d840979922e38d1dc555c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c2378b7a291e44d534884f6b6e7eeb2a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ad4d08daad55de411fe1304fd990b8e3</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773019285</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Natural Persons" target="High-Risk AI System">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Natural persons are responsible for monitoring the operation of high-risk AI systems to ensure their effective use.</data>
  <data key="d9">monitoring,oversight</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-7c2fbe724dee488ea4e437995307241f</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
