<edge source="Natural Persons" target="High-Risk AI Systems">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Natural persons are required to oversee high-risk AI systems and must possess the necessary competence, training, and authority for the role.&lt;SEP&gt;Natural persons may be affected by decisions made by high-risk AI systems and should be informed about their implications.&lt;SEP&gt;Natural persons must be notified when interacting with high-risk AI systems to ensure transparency.&lt;SEP&gt;Natural persons are required to verify and confirm the identification of high-risk AI systems to ensure compliance.</data>
  <data key="d9">affected individuals,authority,competence,information,interaction,oversight,transparency,verification</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-e20d35aae57ccfd5ec58ef7772f98c17&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-46bc64e87ac07d3576c10a8dd9d66d9e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-358eb1d0b0f35e665a7b23702159cfd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-73e4afb71ddc31ffc854d861300d4eb6</data>
  <data key="d11">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d12">1773019306</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
