<edge source="Market Surveillance Authority" target="High-Risk AI System">
  <data key="d7">5.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Market surveillance authorities have the role of overseeing the compliance of high-risk AI systems with established regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;The market surveillance authority may act as a notified body for high-risk AI systems intended for use by regulatory authorities.&lt;SEP&gt;The Market Surveillance Authority assesses whether a high-risk AI system complies with regulatory requirements before authorisation.&lt;SEP&gt;The Market Surveillance Authority is involved in the testing of High-Risk AI Systems upon request from public authorities.&lt;SEP&gt;Market surveillance authorities oversee high-risk AI systems to ensure compliance with EU regulations.</data>
  <data key="d9">authorisation,compliance,compliance check,compliance enforcement,oversight,regulatory compliance,regulatory oversight,regulatory role,testing</data>
