<edge source="Provider" target="High-Risk AI System">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The provider is responsible for ensuring the high-risk AI system complies with regulations and obligations.&lt;SEP&gt;The provider is responsible for ensuring that the high-risk AI system meets compliance with the applicable regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;The provider is responsible for initially placing a high-risk AI system on the market.&lt;SEP&gt;Providers of high-risk AI systems are required to meet specific obligations as outlined in the regulations when placing these systems on the market.</data>
  <data key="d9">compliance,market placement,regulation compliance,regulatory obligations,responsibility</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-4d17f49a76bb2cf6b427b715f614df19&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c3976a157910b9837b3b68c158c5b6b9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-474ee56c196aef9638f343ef09589bca&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20cc9868fcea5ce578101b36c79a42ff</data>
