<edge source="Provider" target="Authorised Representative">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">An authorised representative acts on behalf of a provider, ensuring responsibilities are fulfilled.&lt;SEP&gt;The authorised representative is appointed by the provider to act on its behalf regarding regulatory matters.&lt;SEP&gt;The Provider must appoint an Authorised Representative to aid in fulfilling compliance tasks regarding AI model regulations.</data>
  <data key="d9">appointing authority,compliance,compliance assistance,compliance delegation,representation</data>
