</edge>
<edge source="Provider" target="EU Declaration of Conformity">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The EU Declaration of Conformity is issued by the Provider, confirming the AI system's compliance with regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;The Provider is required to submit a copy of the EU Declaration of Conformity as part of the regulatory compliance process.</data>
  <data key="d9">certification,compliance confirmation,regulatory compliance,regulatory responsibility</data>
