</edge>
<edge source="Provider" target="Notified Body">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The provider may involve a notified body in the assessment of high-risk AI systems as per Annex VII.&lt;SEP&gt;The provider must collaborate with the notified body to assess compliance with the quality management system.&lt;SEP&gt;The Provider must inform the Notified Body of any changes that could affect the compliance or intended purpose of the AI System.&lt;SEP&gt;The Notified Body assesses the Provider's changes and ensures compliance with the quality management system.</data>
  <data key="d9">assessment,assessment process,change notification,compliance,compliance assessment,regulatory oversight</data>
